      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ゼロス・ワイルダーだな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Zelos Wilder, correct?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>15</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>わーお！
勇ましいレディーもいいねぇ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>WOOOOW!
A gallant lady like you is nice, too.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>私の家とも近しい名家の騎士が
貴公に辱めを受けたと訴えている</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A knight from a noble family
close to my own has made the
complaint that you have disgraced him.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>15</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>騎士の誇りを汚す事は何にも勝る狼藉。
もし本当ならば
私は貴公を許せはしない！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>To soil a knight's pride goes far beyond outrage.
If this is the truth, I will not forgive you!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>15</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あーん、凛々しい顔もかわいい！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ahhh, even that imposing face of yours is cute!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>お前！　真面目に話を聞け！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, you! Take what she's saying seriously!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>14</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ごめん。　こういう奴なんだよ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Sorry. This is just how he is...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>10</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>正直に話すつもりはないか。
ならば腕ずくという事になるが？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So you have no intention of
telling me the truth? In that case,
will I have to strong-arm the truth out of you?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>15</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いいんじゃない？
君みたいな可愛い子と
お手合わせできるなんて、光栄だね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's just fine and dandy.
I'd be honored to face a cute girl like you.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ね！　ロイドくん！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Right, Lloyd-kun?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>だからなんで俺に振るんだってば！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So why are you putting me in the front?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes>振る here would be "to substitute", but it'd sound awkward if I had Lloyd saying "So why are you subsituting me for you?!".</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>10</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
